{% call components.section("Usage") -%}

  <p>Modals can be used when critical information requires immediate user attention or for hiding extra content that cannot be displayed due to layout constraints. Modals interrupt user workflows or hide secondary content by design, but should be used sparingly to limit user disruption.</p>

  <h4>Size</h4>

  <p>Container heights and widths will shift responsively depending on the screen size and the amount of content that is included.</p>

