  <div class="margin-top--4">

    <h4>Content vs. video</h4>

    <p>Modals can either organize content that a user can interact with or they can display a large video that a user can watch. A content modal can include smaller videos if they are placed inline with other elements whereas a video player modal features one large video only.</p>

  </div>

